<h3>What's the big idea?</h3>
<p></p>
<h3>What's included?</h3>
<p>Here's what you'll get with your subscription:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Fresh screencasts every Monday</li>
    <li>Video scripts, for those who prefer reading to watching. These are available in Markdown, PDF, OpenOffice, and Microsoft Word formats.</li>
    <li>Full source code for every video, available on GitHub.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Why are they so short?</h3>
<p>My intention is to focus on one piece of Zend Framework 2, without overloading you with too much information. Similar in style to RubyTapas, each lesson aims to do one thing and do it well, without giving you too much to work with. I want you to be able to implement what you learn in each lesson straight-away. Each video comes complete with code, video transcripts and links to further information as relevant, so that you can learn more in your own time.</p>
